---
import SectionTitle from "@/components/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<SectionTitle title="About me" />

<div class="dark:text-neutral-400">
  <p class="text-pretty mb-6">
    I'm a 35-year-old frontend developer based in Murcia, Spain. I work across
    the JavaScript ecosystem — Vue, Angular, and Nuxt on the web, Ionic for
    mobile — and I'm drawn to projects where building the interface well
    actually matters.
  </p>

  <p class="text-pretty mb-6">
    My path into tech was a deliberate choice: I had a degree in building
    engineering, but I chose to start over and complete a vocational
    qualification in web development. That decision shaped how I approach the
    work — I treat learning as something you actively seek out, not something
    that happens to you.
  </p>

  <p class="text-pretty mb-6">
    I'm meticulous about what I put my name on: clear repository structure,
    proper documentation, consistent coding practices. I also enjoy building
    small tools and automations that make daily work more efficient — not
    because it's required, but because that's how I think about software.
  </p>

  <p class="text-pretty">
    What's genuinely energising me right now is the shift in how software gets
    built. I've been actively exploring AI-assisted development — agents, LLMs,
    tools like Claude and Codex — not as a trend to follow but as a real change
    in what a single developer can accomplish.
  </p>
</div>
